{"tid":1135331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男警就學期間瞞擁12幅地皮　涉呃學資處19萬元","createTime":"2019-05-02T08:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T09:05:47.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5d84bad08ae19e888d8b7eeb86a08311107fbb55","tid":1135331,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190502/photo/bkn-20190502155013949-0502_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190502163128\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190502%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190502155013949-0502_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190502163128&h=e593b346&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名男警為大埔梧桐寨村原居民，被揭5年多前求學時期，向學生資助辦事處(現稱學生資助處)申請學費資助，涉嫌隱瞞自己曾因「套丁」而擁有12幅大埔土地，騙得逾19.3萬港元資助，他被控2項欺詐罪，今(2日)在西九龍法院續審，裁判官聽罷辯方結案陳詞，將案押至6月4日裁決。 <br />\n<br />\n辯方結案陳詞指，現年26歲被告古俊輝於2010年事發時剛成年不久，當年「書都未讀完」，遭同村父老游說出售丁權「套丁」。辯方認為「一切似乎事先有安排」，被告只是受人操控，冀法庭考慮被告是否真誠相信「套丁」得來的土地，其實際權益是否歸被告所有，辯方認為存疑點。 <br />\n<br />\n涉案被告古俊輝被控於2013年9月至2014年3月間，及2014年5月至12月間，詐騙學資處根據專上學生資助計劃，分別向他發放約9.39萬港元及約9.94萬港元。被告於案發時就讀香港專業教育學院的銀行及金融高級文憑課程，他於2017年4月已將涉案資助金全數歸還政府。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190502/bkn-20190502155013949-0502_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190502%2Fbkn-20190502155013949-0502_00822_001.html&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJu2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=cf55a7bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190502/bkn-20190502155013949-0502_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"257fe2ba0a9a39c09fef159d98ca167804c4132c","tid":1135331,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:51:32.000Z","msg":"點解咁有錢都要做黑警?"},{"pid":"3f54bb4a3a76b08913ba3e1d25c8008f573eda43","tid":1135331,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍村佬 cross over 郵差 (犯法)"},{"pid":"80db6ed5118b4cc0d75110df1df2098e5f6dbe1e","tid":1135331,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"257fe2ba0a9a39c09fef159d98ca167804c4132c","tid":1135331,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:51:32.000Z","msg":"點解咁有錢都要做黑警?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:53:08.000Z","msg":"識作野先可以升上重要職位，你睇依家班官？"},{"pid":"360a6dfd7d7d4ef41af9b7ccbae64535f9b5a451","tid":1135331,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:53:30.000Z","msg":"套丁賺到嘅錢都夠交學費啦"},{"pid":"b1dcfb84c407f73759636704dfcbc72669714330","tid":1135331,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73de57ba0dbdc96da0dc120e87a753732595d0d3","tid":1135331,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:58:12.000Z","msg":"20萬一個HD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5820a98b24d3e35c977fc5495e345d23c910058e","tid":1135331,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:59:17.000Z","msg":"呢d有錢人應該唔會比人革職<br />\n香港地無人同有錢佬作對 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9992d0d8728cd2f9ac41afcc10020d172ed912","tid":1135331,"uid":73443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T09:00:19.000Z","msg":"想套佢丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feef67f89bf6c4eed86698d8ce38e027ed09997c","tid":1135331,"uid":146243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"360a6dfd7d7d4ef41af9b7ccbae64535f9b5a451","tid":1135331,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:53:30.000Z","msg":"套丁賺到嘅錢都夠交學費啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T09:01:03.000Z","msg":"傻鳩 貪得無厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a54084eeab